1. *Zaspao* sam na poslu juče. (I fell asleep at work yesterday.)
2. On je *zaspao* dok je gledao film. (He fell asleep while watching a movie.)
3. Bilo je kasno kad sam *zaspao* sinoć. (It was late when I fell asleep last night.)
4. Da li si *zaspao* na kraju? (Did you fall asleep in the end?)
5. Ovaj lek će ti pomoći da brže *zaspavaš*. (This medicine will help you fall asleep faster.)
6. Probudio sam se kada je on *zaspao*. (I woke up when he fell asleep.)
7. Nisam mogao *zaspati* zbog buke iz susedne sobe. (I couldn't fall asleep because of the noise from the next room.)
8. Želim da *zaspim* pre ponoći večeras. (I want to fall asleep before midnight tonight.)
9. *Zaspao bih* na plaži kad bih imao vremena. (I would fall asleep on the beach if I had time.)
10. Nisam ni primetio da je on *zaspao*. (I didn't even notice that he had fallen asleep.)